{"tid":1064514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湖北公司加色素生產「化妝走地雞蛋」","createTime":"2019-03-16T15:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T00:46:06.000Z","uid":195944,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6a79db83c4ae818639d928779d4d169ac256945f","tid":1064514,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T15:13:02.000Z","msg":"央視在周五（15日）「國際消費者權益日」舉行晚會，報道多宗有損消費者權益的違規行為。其中有報道稱，湖北蓮田食品開發有限公司出售的聲稱「土雞蛋」（散養走地雞蛋），實際上是籠養雞蛋。央視記者發現，在蓮田的合作養殖場內，全部雞都是養在擠迫的籠裏，但裝雞蛋出售的紙箱都寫上「土雞蛋」。<br />\n<br />\n養殖場負責人表示，雞的飼料加入農業部（現已重組為農業農村部）訂明可用作「飼料着色劑」的「斑蝥黃」，稱這種色素使用量無限制，「只要在適當範圍內，不會影響人體健康」。加入色素的雞蛋蛋黃顏色會變深，之後就會被包裝成「土雞蛋」出售。蓮田銷售經理指出，國家沒為「土雞蛋」訂立標準或權威解釋，故把公司生產的雞蛋說成土雞蛋，也「沒有人管你的」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">蓮田又為生產的雞蛋註冊「鮮土」商標，在包裝寫上「農家鮮土雞蛋」，當中商標的「土」字，與「雞蛋」二字的字型和顏色都極為相似，易令人誤會是「土雞蛋」</span>。同在湖北的神丹健康食品有限公司亦使用類似方式，註冊「好土」商標來出售籠養雞生下的「好土雞蛋」；該公司在央視報道播出後發表聲明，強調「無意於誤導消費者」，並稱「好土」商標今後只會用於公司的散養雞蛋。<br />\n<br />\n（央視/北京晚報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190316/s00004/1552747041847/湖北公司加色素生產「化妝走地雞蛋」-賣貴一兩倍\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190316%2Fs00004%2F1552747041847%2F%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%8A%A0%E8%89%B2%E7%B4%A0%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E3%80%8C%E5%8C%96%E5%A6%9D%E8%B5%B0%E5%9C%B0%E9%9B%9E%E8%9B%8B%E3%80%8D-%E8%B3%A3%E8%B2%B4%E4%B8%80%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8D&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQkwESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=2ac1f3d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8%2Farticle%2F20190316%2Fs00004%2F1552747041847%2F%E6%B9%96%E5%8C%97%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%8A%A0%E8%89%B2%E7%B4%A0%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E3%80%8C%E5%8C%96%E5%A6%9D%E8%B5%B0%E5%9C%B0%E9%9B%9E%E8%9B%8B%E3%80%8D-%E8%B3%A3%E8%B2%B4%E4%B8%80%E5%85%A9%E5%80%8D&h=9118aa77\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/兩岸/article/20190316/s00004/1552747041847/湖北公司加色素生產「化妝走地雞蛋」-賣貴一兩倍</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#haha# 容祖兒童院啲friend"},{"pid":"e326a524495625eec5851548d081f602ad813191","tid":1064514,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"關心研究所<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b150da497d4f9e41027327e639c51cd6aac50e30","tid":1064514,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T15:16:17.000Z","msg":"周華 健身中心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"136a9d5f361e6d4771b818f0b2a44637f475e430","tid":1064514,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7f42251d0d2ec50a484fe02ce97120f8ef7740","tid":1064514,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T15:53:06.000Z","msg":"完成日都有依啲新聞 已經無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e0f2f38b7f863998406cb659d6a970072a12eb","tid":1064514,"uid":128210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:27:13.000Z","msg":"仲有人會以蛋黃顏色黎決定營養價值⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DF1rfiH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDF1rfiH.png&h=92dd8193&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"089d0646e0aec09754a0e483ac08730c2a18356f","tid":1064514,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:56:08.000Z","msg":"有害氣體對人體無害.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n市民喜迎斑蝥黃色素雞蛋.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a63ed50b7fc20ca5bc034002ab83c203ca49774","tid":1064514,"uid":195944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71e0f2f38b7f863998406cb659d6a970072a12eb","tid":1064514,"uid":128210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T16:27:13.000Z","msg":"仲有人會以蛋黃顏色黎決定營養價值⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/